      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "### \u2139\ufe0f About This Report\nSettled monetary transactions and purse-level closing balances from FIS STDMON and STDACCTBAL Data XTRACT feeds. Sourced from **`reporting.fact_monetary`**, **`reporting.fact_account_balance`**, and views **`reporting.vw_daily_monetary_summary`** / **`reporting.vw_daily_purse_balance`**.\n\n| Column | Source | Meaning |\n|--------|--------|--------|\n| Settle Amount | `fact_monetary.settle_amount` | Dollar amount of settled transaction |\n| Txn Type Code | `fact_monetary.txn_type_code` | FIS transaction type (purchase, refund, load, sweep) |\n| Purse Code | `fact_monetary.purse_code` | Which purse was debited (OTC2100, FOD2100, CMB2100) |\n| Work of Date | `fact_monetary.work_of_date` | Reporting date the transaction belongs to |\n| Closing Balance | `fact_account_balance.closing_balance` | Purse balance at end of reporting day |\n| Opening Balance | `fact_account_balance.opening_balance` | Purse balance at start of reporting day |\n| Total Purchase Amount | `fact_account_balance.total_purchase_amount` | Sum of all purchases that day |\n| Total Valueload Amount | `fact_account_balance.total_valueload_amount` | Sum of all loads that day |\n\n> \u26a0\ufe0f **This report requires FIS STDMON and STDACCTBAL XTRACT feeds to be active.** Pending DM-03 confirmation from Kendra Williams.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.4.3",
      "title": "",
      "type": "text"
    },
